<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span style="color:#008000">(٠٠٠ - ٧٧٤ هـ)</span> <span style="color:#008000">(٠٠٠ - ١٣٧٢ م)</span><a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
